{"tid":1015780,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日傳奇2-4季","createTime":"2019-02-10T10:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T21:43:05.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8eed46cccb0df69eeea644d97d13734b3126211d","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=5e4c09dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=c8734444\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=a5485fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://godhatesgeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LoT-Feature.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgodhatesgeeks.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2FLoT-Feature.png&h=2c80dd57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png%3Alarge&h=e6451025&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://cdn.spoilertv.com/images/headers/legends.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.spoilertv.com%2Fimages%2Fheaders%2Flegends.jpg&h=0616d357&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/video_poster/2018/2018100310015320807d73d8dbf19dc4fc3188a56928524018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fvideo_poster%2F2018%2F2018100310015320807d73d8dbf19dc4fc3188a56928524018.jpg&h=5c1d327a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.由於時間領主總部摧毀，傳奇們被迫擔負起修復歷史的使命。然而他們也擔心時俠的警告，傳奇們發現Damien Darhk於1942年的時候企圖發射核武炸毀紐約。<br />\n而Damien Darhk更與逆閃電及黑箭等組成「末日軍團」。逆閃電協助末日軍團的目的就是要防止神速力怪物的追捕<br />\n<br />\n2.在2017年洛杉磯看到時間大亂的傳奇團隊，最後發現原來已經離開的Rip Hunter成立了時間管理局替代時間領主。原來在他離開後發覺他們打亂了時間，於是就成立了時間管理局來解決事件。在2017年，時間管理局規模已經十分宏大。<br />\n同時，Rip Hunter也宣布傳奇解散。Sara回到星城，並在一間衛浴店超市里工作。火風暴、鋼鐵隊長則回到中城，鋼鐵隊長成為了該地排第二的超級英雄。而火風暴的兩人則繼續他們的生活。Jax繼續進修大學，而Martin則與他因修復時間而產生的副作用&mdash;&mdash;他的女兒Lily等共享天倫。Ray則在矽谷工作。Amaya則回到1942年她的小山村。Mick Rory則在阿魯巴度假<br />\n<br />\n3.五個月後，傳奇解決了所有時間錯誤。但時間線外的魔法生物開始出現影響時間線，魔法顧問康斯坦汀：驅魔神探及變形怪Charlie加入了傳奇小隊。另一方面，時間管理局為因應魔法生物的出現也開始建立防範機制，Nate為了逃避情傷也加入了時間管理局與Ave共事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=bb9d44d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=0da43e6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17fc3579713ee9473dd3fbe86aecae543cd25db","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f3e467afba071d9d017c15d6be3ed3cacd02c","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9596ce1353615c26183900d61cd7a0dec836a528","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032ba4aba35c46e001c37c9870a936d219ce94eb","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c887fb56b804f49e07a798fddda37b3e49d6fae","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775cc738406d2252aa1756fb54e80f822a01973e","tid":1015780,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bce27b0433f975fb98c39410e493520e404705c","tid":1015780,"uid":57647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":